message.content:
There is a kitchen area and a dining room area. The kitchen area has a taupe-colored marble countertop with dark-brown cabinets. On top of the countertop, there are two puzzle boxes, a jar of jam, a yellow cup, a pot on a stove, and plates stacked on top of each other. A sink is built into the left side of the countertop. A white refrigerator is along the wall to the right of the countertop. A dark-brown cabinet is above the countertop, while below it are dark-brown drawers. A vent hood is on the ceiling. A doorway leads to the dining room. 

The dining room area has a rectangular wooden table with four white upholstered chairs. The table has a bottle of water with a pyramid of plastic cups on top and a plate with fruit on it and a cookbook on top. There are white walls with a door and empty picture frames on it. 

The floor in both rooms is made of wood parquet.
